entry.title: 2 Bedroom Flat, 163 New Kings Road
entry.propertyDescription:
A spacious, furnished, one bedroom apartment situated on the first floor of a handsome refurbished Edwardian building. Situated on the Peterborough Estate on New Kings Road with views over Eel Brook common from the reception room.

The property comprises of an entrance hall, reception with open plan kitchen including built in fridge freezer, electric hob & gas oven, dishwasher and washer dryer, large double bedroom with an ensuite shower room, bathroom with power shower over bath and a good size study/ second bedroom.

Less than a 5 minute walk to either Fulham Broadway or Parsons Green tube station.
